Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.19,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要與你一同將門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:22.38,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}許個願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.52,ED-CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}最愛的那個地方
